LMS_Improvements: I would like to see the platform as an app. While website is okay, app would be much more accessible and easier to use even with bad internet connection.
LMS_Convenience_Explained: Only thing inconvenient is my connection and electricity. The rest is fine.
Mentor_Experience: I felt enlighten. I learned things that I previously had no idea about.
GED_Improvements: Instructor engagement and interaction
GED_Improvement_Recommendations: More interactive activities or group work, Access to online resources or recorded lessons, More personalized feedback on assessments
Top_GED_Contributors: Quality of teaching and instruction, Availability of practice exams and quizzes, Motivation and encouragement from teacher
Additional_Comments: I am genuinely satisfied with the program. I find the learning platform a bit hard to access. I hope to see easier, more accessible and improved version of the platform.
Requested_Topics: I ,personally,hope to see the additional courses like intensive course or exam preparation course for students who want to take the exam after the program.
Experiences_Shares: Overall experience is fun and engaging.
